metadata.name: find, saved Lu
metadata.description:
Lu Ming and Li Ping have been living together since six years ago when it was reported that his father was killed while traveling outside.



Lu Ming looked at Li Ping, the eyes changed soft up, way: "Niang, nothing, just a dream."



Looking at Lu Ming's pale face, Li Ping sat beside Lu Ming's bed, touching Lu Ming's forehead, heartache of the way: "has been three days, every time you cry out Lu Yao harm you, Ming Son, in the end is how to return a responsibility? Is your injury because of Lu Yao..."
